      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">2</infon>
        <offset>70</offset>
        <text>Fertilization of the ocean by adding iron compounds has induced diatom-dominated phytoplankton blooms accompanied by considerable carbon dioxide drawdown in the ocean surface layer.
</text>
