          <infon key="brat-id">E5</infon>
          <node refid="T5" role="Decrease"/>
          <node refid="T10" role="Theme"/>
        </relation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">7</infon>
        <offset>883</offset>
        <text>Taken together, multiple lines of evidence--although each with important uncertainties--lead us to conclude that at least half the bloom biomass sank far below a depth of 1,000 metres and that a substantial portion is likely to have reached the sea floor.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">8</infon>
        <offset>1139</offset>
        <text>Thus, iron-fertilized diatom blooms may sequester carbon for timescales of centuries in ocean bottom water and for longer in the sediments.
</text>
